Package: cruisecontrolrb
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, adduser, mongrel, ruby, rake
Recommends: subversion, git-core, mercurial
Description: a continuous integration tool. 
 Its basic purpose in life is to alert members of a software project 
 when one of them checks something into source control that breaks the build. 
 .
 See <http://cruisecontrolrb.thoughtworks.com/> for more info.

